```

### Release Process

```bash
# 1. Sync main
git checkout main
git pull origin main

# 2. Create release tag
git tag v1.2.0
git push origin v1.2.0

# 3. Create GitHub release
# (via interface or GitHub CLI)
gh release create v1.2.0 --generate-notes
```

